{"tid":787089,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴黎露天尿兜惹爭議，女權：強化只有男人站著痾尿的形象","createTime":"2018-08-20T11:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T14:08:30.000Z","uid":27240,"like":19,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5651c933e907ae41ecc4fbe9ffc4670e9d28ead3","tid":787089,"uid":27240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"浪漫之都的巴黎裝上了露天的尿兜，還做到了生態環保沒有揮發性的味道，但就是露天的那種，你敢去試一試嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/20/193650_c7ead317578168d5a3f709932647036d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2F193650_c7ead317578168d5a3f709932647036d.jpg&h=47432b57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據報導，為了解決隨地小便發出陣陣的尿騷味問題，法國巴黎政府在塞納河邊安裝了露天尿兜，他們的位置大多位於遊客聚集的區域 ，然而沒有任何遮擋措施，一使用便會陷入「被圍觀」尷尬的尿兜遭到了大家的爭議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/20/193722_7e0511c3baf2f10c67a7a068b547a841.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2F193722_7e0511c3baf2f10c67a7a068b547a841.jpg&h=fcf5cf32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實，露天尿兜設計的理念很生態環保，內部收集堆肥提供養料，頂部用來種植花草，富餘的部分可用於公園內的其它綠植，當尿液積滿時，外部的傳感器就會發出蜂鳴，管理人員便會來處理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/20/193806_90c056ecc1bb1f7dcce4fdc3b10f3b4d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2F193806_90c056ecc1bb1f7dcce4fdc3b10f3b4d.jpeg&h=c1ec79f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過露天尿兜大多位於景區地方，大家表示這樣的品味未免太低級，大煞風景，惹來不少的爭議。另外，女權組織也強烈抗議，她們認為露天尿兜更加強化了只有男人們可以站著痾尿的專屬形象。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/20/193825_abec124464555ee2267f2f309c51b538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2F193825_abec124464555ee2267f2f309c51b538.jpg&h=b89256a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴黎市政府表示設立這些新廁所的初衷，完全是考慮到該區域日趨增多的對公共廁所的需求。但現在爭議重重，恐怕這些原有露天尿兜難保，被撤走的機率很大。<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2018/08/20/uritrottoir/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2Furitrottoir%2F&d=63RKd3urOAr6ZlDprLlRoO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=f7b4fb05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2018/08/20/uritrottoir/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nD 女權撚真係好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30650dd9467331a57abc1d71123b69e6713f8cc2","tid":787089,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T11:41:49.000Z","msg":"吹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747a200695c04cd9b54e3f418312109b5a7b06e4","tid":787089,"uid":27240,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T13:11:28.000Z","msg":"女權撚好煩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2745dc76c16896b84f63c3285d3d5c8d4d197882","tid":787089,"uid":16414,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T13:23:02.000Z","msg":"女權組織也強烈抗議，她們認為露天尿兜更加強化了只有男人們可以站著痾尿的專屬形象。<br />\n<br />\n你地都可以企係度屙尿架喎, 有禁止過咩"},{"pid":"3d8247c769ebdaeb196c50770b43188a597ff966","tid":787089,"uid":21545,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T13:28:42.000Z","msg":"女權撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁得閑 不如去中東同印度救下嗰度啲女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c730dd345fdfe30354a8ff703c413704c66ddac","tid":787089,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T13:31:34.000Z","msg":"生理結構唔同咁都好嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247bfe9dfd518e2f5d160c84755805aab87c3218","tid":787089,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike